1.000Z","msg":"呢個係人類嘅本性<br />\n毒品同賭博基本上都係同樣性質<br />\n就係會令人上癮<br />\n分別只係一樣係犯法，另一樣可以係合法<br />\n呢兩樣嘢大部份人都極易使人上癮，而上咗癮之後<br />\n都會不能自拔，失卻理性<br />\n亦因物理性質如此<br />\n做毒同開賭嘅大莊，都係必然會大賺<br />\n賭枱上（股，馬，波）長遠上贏到錢嘅老散<br />\n我相信九成九都係賭癮唔大<br />\n即係可以控制到自己嘅心癮<br />\n純粹理性技術機會率操作行先<br />\n不過呢種人，比例上係極少"},{"pid":"953c9bb6c71c0b3282a7f436db8bf16866bb56ea","tid":1002110,"uid":37747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:10:34.000Z","msg":"你朋友就係"},{"pid":"7c029328b4886f762fd51ca2661191617c6dfd50","tid":1002110,"uid":123787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你朋友就係</blockquote><br />\n不是我<br />\n是我既話唔會咁大篇文"},{"pid":"16e5a46991d0f539b6745551681bcb0ad136a0cf","tid":1002110,"uid":52271,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"就咁睇黎就係佢老母唔好好睇住個仔<br />\n出左事又屌唔落自己，是但搵個人黎屌<br />\n但當中仲有幾多細節就唔知喇"},{"pid":"ed2ed79b713fd4f0b68a42935e199601e195d16d","tid":1002110,"uid":123787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968204f9269f613e799dc98094b1cc21eeb54367","tid":1002110,"uid":15370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:29:24.000Z","msg":"點解要陪佢賭？"},{"pid":"ec8b00772187ab8e1836768ea589b55bd12720a9","tid":1002110,"uid":8636,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:30:41.000Z","msg":"點解輸左錢要無啦啦吞精？心"},{"pid":"6511381734ff4f9feed7996367b74d0e5b542a7e","tid":1002110,"uid":26773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"95c96e6f6d97faa7b69ecf2b922cffe5289e0e05","tid":1002110,"uid":59333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:05:06.000Z","msg":"想睇相"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08dece05370e1b20f9e331b9644302b5ca18c68","tid":1002110,"uid":189109,"like